casebody.data:
Judith KILLMER and Robert Killmer, Plaintiffs-Appellants,
v.
Donald J. SABOURIN, D.D.S., P.L.L.C., and Joel Hayden, D.D.S., Defendants-Appellees. SC: 156487
COA: 337338 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 1, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the August 14, 2017 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
